@startuml
title Company Creation — AI Chat to Provisioning Saga
autonumber

skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FDF6E3
skinparam noteBorderColor #657B83
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam participantPadding 10
skinparam BoxPadding 10

actor "Admin FE\n(Angular)" as FE
participant "Gateway\n(YARP)" as GW
participant "AI Service v2" as AI
participant "OpenAI API" as OAI
participant "Monolith MCP" as MCP
database "Monolith DB\n(SQL Server)" as MODB
participant "Monolith API\n(Core System of Record)" as MON
participant "Outbox Processor" as OBX
participant "Provisioning Connector\n(Saga Orchestrator)" as CON
participant "User API" as USR
participant "Company API" as CMP
participant "Job API" as JOB
participant "Keycloak" as KC

note over FE,KC
**Scenario:** Admin says "Create a company called Acme Corp"
AI selects create_company tool, provisions across 7 services in ~5.5s
end note

== Phase 1 — Chat request and tool selection ==

FE -> GW: POST /ai/v2/chat
activate GW
GW -> AI: proxy -> ai-service-v2
activate AI

AI -> OAI: POST /v1/chat/completions
activate OAI
note right of OAI
Tool selection
~1,601ms
end note
OAI --> AI: tool_call: create_company
deactivate OAI

== Phase 2 — MCP tool execution + CQRS command pipeline ==

AI -> MCP: tools/call -> create_company
activate MCP

MCP -> MODB: Validate (~60ms)
note right of MODB
Company name uniqueness
Company email uniqueness
Admin email uniqueness
Industry existence
end note
MODB --> MCP: valid

MCP -> MODB: Atomic transaction (~234ms)
note right of MODB
INSERT Company
INSERT User
INSERT Outbox message
Single commit
end note
MODB --> MCP: committed

note right of MCP
Monolith MCP shares the monolith
codebase and DB connection.
No HTTP call to Monolith API.
end note

MCP --> AI: tool result (success, ~531ms)
deactivate MCP

AI -> OAI: POST /v1/chat/completions
activate OAI
note right of OAI
Response generation
~1,292ms
end note
OAI --> AI: "Company created..."
deactivate OAI

AI --> GW: 200 OK (streamed)
note right of GW
User-facing response completes here.
Provisioning continues asynchronously.
end note
deactivate AI

GW --> FE: chat response
deactivate GW

== Phase 4 — Outbox to pub/sub ==

OBX -> MODB: Poll outbox
MODB --> OBX: message #790 (company.created.v1)

OBX -> CON: Dapr pub/sub\ncompany.created.v1 (CloudEvent)

OBX -> MODB: Mark processed

== Phase 5 — Provisioning saga fetches source-of-truth data ==

activate CON
note over CON: Idempotency check (~3ms)

CON -> MON: GET /odata/companies({id})
activate MON
MON --> CON: 200 company data
deactivate MON

CON -> MON: GET /odata/users({id})
activate MON
MON --> CON: 200 admin data
deactivate MON

note over CON
Saga fetch phase complete
~232ms
end note

== Phase 6 — Parallel fan-out via Dapr service invocation ==

par Dapr -> user-api (~1,440ms)
  CON -> USR: POST /api/companies\n(Dapr invoke)
  activate USR

  == Phase 7 — Identity provisioning in Keycloak (~1,389ms) ==

  USR -> KC: GET /groups
  activate KC
  KC --> USR: 200 (12ms)
  deactivate KC

  USR -> KC: POST /groups/.../children\n(company group)
  activate KC
  KC --> USR: 201 (19ms)
  deactivate KC

  USR -> KC: POST /groups/.../children\n(CompanyAdmins)
  activate KC
  KC --> USR: 201 (14ms)
  deactivate KC

  USR -> KC: POST /groups/.../children\n(Recruiters)
  activate KC
  KC --> USR: 201 (9ms)
  deactivate KC

  USR -> KC: GET /users (check existing)
  activate KC
  KC --> USR: 200 (10ms)
  deactivate KC

  USR -> KC: POST /users (create user)
  activate KC
  KC --> USR: 201 (269ms)
  deactivate KC

  USR -> KC: PUT /users/{id}/groups/{gid}
  activate KC
  KC --> USR: 204 (12ms)
  deactivate KC

  USR -> KC: PUT /users/{id}/send-verify-email
  activate KC
  KC --> USR: 204 (36ms)
  deactivate KC

  note over USR
Persist user + company records
~987ms
end note

  USR --> CON: 200 OK
  deactivate USR

else Dapr -> company-api (~1,133ms)
  CON -> CMP: POST /api/companies\n(Dapr invoke)
  activate CMP
  note over CMP: Create company projection
  CMP --> CON: 200 OK
  deactivate CMP

else Dapr -> job-api (~268ms)
  CON -> JOB: POST /api/companies\n(Dapr invoke)
  activate JOB
  note over JOB: Create company projection
  JOB --> CON: 204 No Content
  deactivate JOB
end

== Phase 8 — Company activation ==

USR ->> CON: pub/sub\nprovision.user.success

CON -> MON: POST /api/companies/company-created-success
activate MON
MON -> MODB: ActivateCompanyCommand (~128ms)
note right of MODB
UPDATE Company.Status = Active
UPDATE User.ExternalId
end note
MODB --> MON: committed
MON --> CON: 200 OK

== Phase 9 — Real-time notification ==

MON ->> FE: SignalR: CompanyActivated\n(~3ms send + receive)
deactivate MON

note over FE
UI updates in real time:
company.name = "Acme Corp"
end note

== Phase 10 — Saga complete ==

note over CON
Saga finalized
Company fully provisioned
end note
deactivate CON

@enduml